channel.description:
Hello moparscape(: i am looking for a development team that is going to be successful.. or is already successful(: I'm looking for a coding development position so if you could add me on msn: Austin_clay_newton@hotmail.com. I've been/still looking for a development team.. not a single job development, last one i was on he went to school and i sat there coding a server then coding another.. and yeah.. its complicated, i want i orginized development team! Please!!!!!!!!!!
[center]Tabel of Content[/center] [center]What I Can Code[/center] [center]How Long I've Been Coding[/center] [center]Pictures of clients and sources i've developed today 4/9/2011[/center] [center]Hope you enjoy these fantastic messages of me, lol(:[/center]
[center]What I Can Code/How I Can Help[/center] I can code a list of things. texts all the way to shops/npcs. I can make a training area, shops(only if there is shops on there unless it would take me a long time), KBD, dragons, anything u name it but they might not have the right stats as Runescape but thats why its not called RUNESCAPE!!! Ppl need to learn that -.-...
[center]How Long I've Been Coding[/center] I've started out on runescape playing that for a year.. but out of no where i got bored, and i found this from one of my friends in 6th grade (I'm in 8th now). So we joined servers everyone did and we never knew how they made them. So like 5 months later (I'm smarter than my friends but still smoke weed with them and shiz) i go on hamachi and go on a server. I ask the owner to teach me how to code, he tought me the basic how to change the name. So i kept downloading and downloading files till my computer got a virus.. i'm sure some of u out there have done that lol(:, now i've started back up nowing how to code(: well thats the end(:
These are just pictures to show you that i can code, this is not even close to what i can make.
